														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1375325">
									

<p>In my headcanon, the written form is always &quot;SCP&quot; (with very few exceptions [edit: exceptions like literal transcripts]), and it can be pronounced either &quot;Ess See Pee&quot; or &quot;Scip&quot; depending on who you're talking to, as well as what you're taking about (example: <a href="/i-wanna-be-the-very-best">SCPokemon</a> sounds really weird pronounced &quot;Scipkemon&quot;, but just fine as &quot;Ess See Pokemon&quot;).</p>

